Installation
============

  Short Instructions
  ------------------
  1. Build and install Python (1.5 or newer)
  2. Build and install the LZO library (1.03 or newer)
  3. Run "./configure"
  4. Edit the file `Setup' if you've installed the LZO library
       in an unusal place
  5. Run "make"
  6. Test the module by runnning "python ./test.py"
  7. Optional: run "strip lzomodule.so"
  8. Run "make install" to install the module (when logged in as root)


See Makefile.pre.in for more possible configuration details.

